name: 私自身
description:
"Who have I killed?"
"Who do I see in the reflection of the water in the sink?"
"I think she can help me."
"Can I live?"
"I wonder, what inside of me?"
"I see someone!" "I am her!" "No, she is me!"
"Who am I?"
"Who have I killed?"

Crisis. She facing it by her own self, trying to be someone, and its killing her.
